						<summary>

						<p>Madurai Nāyaka, Tirumalai-nāyaka, Śaka 1560, Pramādi, Āni 16 = A.D. 1639.</p>						

						<p>This records gift of the village of Tirumalasamudram to the temple of Chokkanāthasvāmi for conducting certain festivals in the months of Tai, Vaiyāsi, and Āṉi for the merit of (the king) Tirumalai-Nāyakkar, a descendant of Viśvanātha-Nāyakkar.</p>						

